of so many deities, and specially one form of=\r\n the Mother. The upward triangle is our aspiration, the downward is Her gra=\r\nce coming down to transform the sadhak from his/her current state. Together=\r\n, it makes a complete whole. And grace is purely proportional to the purity=\r\n of the aspiration, which only God can\n judge\n&gt; &gt;  accurately.\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; -Re=\r\ngards\n&gt; &gt; =C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82=C2=A0Rajarshi \n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; awaktam wyakti=\r\nmApannam manyantE mAmabuddhayah |\n&gt; &gt; param bhAwamajAnanto mamAwyayamanutta=\r\nmam ||[7:24]\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; ________________________________\n&gt; &gt;  From: ashu=\r\ntosh.srikanth &lt;ashutosh.srikanth@&gt;\n&gt; &gt; To: vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com \n&gt; =\r\n&gt; Sent: Monday, 22 October 2012 5:17 PM\n&gt; &gt; Subject: [vedic-wisdom] Homam -=\r\n Ahuti numbers\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; =C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82=C2=A0 \n&gt; &gt; My pranams to=\r\n all.\n&gt; &gt; I have been performing weekly havan for more than a year and half=\r\n.\n&gt; &gt; I want to point out certain things related to havan so that it can be=\r\n done as per shastra by others too.\n&gt; &gt; I am using a conversation that in f=\r\nact took place to bring out these relevant points.\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; Sometime back t=\r\nhere was informal &quot;prashNa&quot; session whose summary I am presenting below: \n&gt;=\r\n &gt; \n&gt; &gt; [South Indians might be familiar with similar &quot;ashTamangala prashNa=\r\n&quot; conducted in temples when something goes wrong - called as dosha.]\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt;=\r\n &gt; PrashNa conductor: There seems to be a dosha... Hmm... let me see... Hmm=\r\n.. Yes... You seem to be performing some kind of Agni karya at your home re=\r\ngularly.\n&gt; &gt; \n&gt; &gt; Myself: Yes (I was actually very surprised by this pointe=\r\nd question because I had not told anybody about the havan I did at home)\n&gt; =\r\n&gt; \n&gt; &gt; PrashNa cond